    Was CP1 passed?
        │
   ┌────┴────┐
  YES       NO
   │         │
   ↓         ↓
[CP2 OK]  [INVALID]
 mark      show
 passed   warning
   │
   ↓
[Check finish]
        │
   All CPs passed?
